description: Henri & Dyandra, with their collective restaurant experience and mutual passion for food and service, are trucking through Atlanta and tempting every palate around with their soulfully delicious cajun and creole cuisine.They’re serving up wonderfully tasty Po’Boys, Jambalaya, Etouffee, Shrimp & Grits, and other delightful dishes. You can also find scrumptious homemade flatbread pizza by the slice, and a delectable breakfast selection that includes homemade buttery biscuits, pancakes, burritos, and more.For a taste of these delightful eats, be sure to follow this fabulous truck and perhaps invite to feed your friends at your next fun party!
name: The Tempted Palate Food Truck & Catering
